        },
        name: "Margaret Sims",
        comment: "On&nbsp;my&nbsp;way to&nbsp;the hotel, I&nbsp;checked the email and clicked to&nbsp;the link to&nbsp;get to&nbsp;the app&nbsp;&mdash; my&nbsp;information was logged in, I&nbsp;did not have to&nbsp;do&nbsp;a&nbsp;thing, just order some food which was waiting for me&nbsp;by&nbsp;the time I&nbsp;got to&nbsp;the room.",
